un mayne tsvey shvesters hobn shoyn do gevoynt. un der bruder fun Erets-Yisroel hot oykh a shtikl tsayt demolts do gevoynt.

00:12:42.386 --> 00:12:47.089
un ikh hob demolts RETIREt in Vin,

00:12:47.212 --> 00:12:50.565
bin ikh gekumen aher tsu di mishpokhe, mir zo'mir zayn tsuzamen.

00:12:50.857 --> 00:12:52.893
un vu in Nyu-York voynstu?

00:12:52.764 --> 00:12:55.813
in Nyu-York voyn ikh in Kvins,

00:12:56.291 --> 00:12:57.892
di genoye adrese

00:12:57.892 --> 00:13:00.473
iz ha-

00:12:59.851 --> 00:13:01.957
FOREST HILLS

00:13:00.473 --> 00:13:02.394
vi? FOREST HILLS, yo.

00:13:02.619 --> 00:13:05.786
un ven hostu gekumen do tsu MIAMI BEACH?

00:13:05.589 --> 00:13:07.997
MIAMI BEACH bin ikh nor do in vinter.

00:13:08.559 --> 00:13:10.244
dos ze'mir shoyn do,

00:13:10.263 --> 00:13:13.548
fifte zekste yor vos mir ze'mir do in vinter.

00:13:14.347 --> 00:13:17.514
du host mir gevolt zogn epes fun der rebe,

00:13:18.414 --> 00:13:20.433
frier du host geganen tsu AUSCHWITZ.

00:13:19.612 --> 00:13:21.969
fun Koloshitser rebe, yo.

00:13:22.329 --> 00:13:25.496
ven mir ze'mir gevezn in tsug un m'iz ongekumen

00:13:25.788 --> 00:13:27.386
shabes mitog,

00:13:28.117 --> 00:13:29.006
nokh,

00:13:28.151 --> 00:13:30.457
dos iz ven du host aroysgeganen fun

00:13:30.345 --> 00:13:32.162
neyn. neyn, neyn, befor.

00:13:30.537 --> 00:13:32.554
fun fun di UNK, yo.

00:13:32.724 --> 00:13:36.296
befor m'iz, me hot, m'iz oysgeshtign fun tsug,

00:13:36.437 --> 00:13:40.667
hot er gemakht havdole, s'iz gevezn nokh khtsos, shabes,

00:13:40.993 --> 00:13:43.873
un er hot gezogt mitn gantsn oylem vide.

00:13:45.532 --> 00:13:48.058
er hot shoyn gevust vos es tut zikh do.

00:13:53.885 --> 00:13:56.546
dos iz gevezn mitn Koloshitser rebn.

00:13:59.488 --> 00:14:01.794
er iz geven zeyer zeyer a voyler yid.

00:14:03.065 --> 00:14:04.916
an emesdiker erlekher yid.

00:14:07.892 --> 00:14:14.164
IF du vilst, IF du vilst zogn epes tsu di yingere kinder vos lebn haynt un vos vet lebn morgn,

00:14:14.777 --> 00:14:16.121
vos vilstu zogn?

00:14:15.350 --> 00:14:23.782
yo, vel ikh zogn, ets zolts enk nisht lozn narish makhn fun dey vos zey zogn az s'iz nisht gevezn gornisht, dos iz ales emes vos ikh hob ertseylt.

00:14:24.665 --> 00:14:25.911
un dos iz

00:14:25.911 --> 00:14:27.494
toyres-emes,

00:14:27.686 --> 00:14:31.157
s'iz gor keyn shum vort iz nishto keyn lignt in dem.

00:14:33.980 --> 00:14:36.163
un far der velt vos vilstu zogn?

00:14:36.427 --> 00:14:39.172
genoy dos zelbe zog ikh far der velt oykh.

00:14:39.785 --> 00:14:44.431
az di ale zakhn vos di natsis zogn haynt, di neo-natsis,

00:14:44.431 --> 00:14:47.914
dos iz ales lignt un yimakh-shmom-vezikhrom.

00:14:48.577 --> 00:14:55.912
un emes iz dos az der Oyshvits hot ekzistirt un s- un dey ale zakhn iz pasirt azoy vi ikh hob es ertseylt.

00:14:57.960 --> 00:15:01.431
MISTER Yosef Kats, a groysn dank tsu dir,

00:15:02.668 --> 00:15:05.582
far alts vos du host mir haynt gezogt,

00:15:07.207 --> 00:15:10.256
un ⟨farn⟩ dayn gantse mishpokhe vos lebt nisht.

00:15:10.700 --> 00:15:11.724
OK.

00:15:12.490 --> 00:15:13.630
a groysn dank.

00:15:16.455 --> 00:15:17.783
dos iz es.
